data.description: Custom-Built by Jimmy Bryan in Park Place! Corner lot with side entry garage. Isolated Master suite with walk in closet & private bath with shower. 2 more spacious bedrooms with plenty of closet space and share a full bath and doors to separate this area from the rest of home if desired. When you walk in the front door you enter a spacious foyer that leads into the LR w/fireplace which also is open to the dining room and the kitchen. Details are TOO many to try to list. Hardwood floors, crown molding, tile, backspace, built ins, and so much more!! Sweet little study in hallway to master suite. Large garage covered porches. Total Sq Ft is 2425 w/garage. NEW ROOF 10/26/2023 -1 yr Home Warranty
